OrderBite
OrderBite, formerly known as ace-blue-box, is a comprehensive food ordering platform that connects customers with their favorite restaurants. Built with modern technologies, OrderBite offers a seamless and user-friendly experience for browsing menus, placing orders, and managing transactions.

Table of Contents
-> Project Overview
-> Features
-> Technologies Used
-> Usage
-> Contact

Project Overview
OrderBite is designed to simplify the food ordering process, providing a sleek interface where users can easily find restaurants, customize their orders, and track their deliveries. Whether you're craving a quick bite or a full meal, OrderBite ensures a satisfying experience with just a few clicks.

Features
-> User Authentication & Registration: Secure login and sign-up processes using Auth0.
-> Search, Sort, Filter, & Pagination: Easily find restaurants and dishes based on your preferences.
-> Restaurant Management: Manage restaurant profiles and upload images using Cloudinary.
-> Cart & Stripe Checkout: Seamless and secure checkout experience with Stripe integration.
-> Live Order Status: Stay updated on your orderâ€™s progress in real-time.
-> Responsive Design: Optimized for all devices, ensuring a smooth experience on desktops, tablets, and mobile phones.

Technologies Used
-> Frontend: React, Tailwind CSS, Shadcn
-> Backend: Node.js, Express, MongoDB
-> Languages: JavaScript, TypeScript
-> Authentication: Auth0
-> Payments: Stripe
-> Image Management: Cloudinary
-> Deployment: Render
-> Version Control: GitHub

Usage
-> Search for Restaurants: Use the search bar to find restaurants by name, cuisine, or location.
-> Customize Orders: Browse menus, select dishes, and customize your order.
-> Secure Checkout: Review your order and complete the payment using Stripe.
-> Track Your Order: Stay informed with live updates on your order status.

